    <item>
      <title>中国或将继续尝试刺激消费，但不采取大规模刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/china-will-keep-trying-to-spur-consumption-without-big-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国高层领导人已暗示将采取更强有力的刺激措施，以填补消费需求缺口。但这并不意味着北京方面会立即推出“火箭筒式”刺激计划，或放弃对制造业的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/china-will-keep-trying-to-spur-consumption-without-big-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
